metadata.name: Proof Of Puff #001
metadata.description:
This NFT commemorates you being part of the first-ever Proof Of Puff strain drop at the legendary Fight Klub Studios in NYC! This is the first of many incoming Proof of Puff strain drops, so thank you for believing in the project and movement! 

Shoutouts to our project partners Tai Ku Labs, W3BBIE, Dr. Green, Puffer Gang, Uptown Terps, DotConnector, Proof of Vibes, Loudpack, Happy Munkey, and the entire Proof of Puff Team! 

Big thank you to R0seNY (Founder of the Puffer Gang) for the artwork! 

To activate the AR experience please head to: https://www.instagram.com/ar/1159991347947119/
